text: Trapped by G-Men is a 1937 American crime film directed by Lewis D. Collins and starring Jack Holt, Wynne Gibson, and C. Henry Gordon. ==Cast== *Jack Holt as Martin Galloway *Wynne Gibson as Alice Segar *C.
